
'''Lucy Anin ('''Wɔ woo no June da ɛtɔ so 13, afe 1939) Ghanani amanyɔni. ɔyɛ Kane mmarahyɛ baguani a ogyinaa ho maa Bono ne Ahafo mantam mu foɔ firi afe 1960 kosi 1965 na afe, mmarahyɛ badwani a ogyina hɔ ma Bechem mpesoa so firi afe 1965 kosi 1966

== N'asetena mu ne Amanyɔsɛm ==
Anin ka mmaa a wodikan nyaa akwanya kɔɔ mmarahyɛ badwa mu wɔ afe 1960, a na wogyina hɔ sɛ mmaa anamusifo. ɔka mmaa du a wɔpaw wɔn a w’anto aba anyi wɔn wo afe 1960 sɛ wongyina ma wonpere mmarahyɛ bagua wɔ amanyɔkuo Conventions People din mu

ɔbɛyɛɛ mmarahyɛ baguani a osua koraa a w’anya akwanya akɔ mmarahyɛ bagua mu, na w’adi mfie 21. Wɔ afe 1965 mu no, ɔbɛyɛɛ mmarahyɛ badwani a ogyina hɔ ma Bechem mpɛsoa so. Wɔ afe 1966 mu bre a wotuu Nkruma aban gui no, wo de no too afiase boseme 8 a na w’afa afuro. ɛnnɛ, ɔka mpanyinfoɔ wodi amanyɔkuo Conventions People Party no anim, na ɔno nkoa ne ɔbaa a w’aka wɔ mma 10 a wodii kan hyen mmarahyɛ badwa mu wɔ adehyeman Ghana a edi kan.

